---
// How It Works Section
// "Refine the problem. Define the solution."
// Includes Product Surface Foundation diagram
---

<section class="how-it-works section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="big-bold-text">REFINE THE PROBLEM. DEFINE THE SOLUTION.</h2>

    <p class="intro-text">
      Every product is different. Every business has unique patterns. We don't rush discovery—we do it right.
    </p>

    <div class="process-overview">
      <h3>The Process:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>As many proof-of-concepts as needed (typically 5-7 maximum)</li>
        <li>Each PoC validates one assumption, tests one unknown</li>
        <li>Research-driven, user-validated methodology</li>
        <li>Time-based contract ensures thoroughness</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="methodology">
      <h3>Our Methodology:</h3>
      <p class="methodology-intro">
        Starting from your business foundation, we layer discovery:
      </p>

      <div class="foundation-stack" id="foundation-stack">
        <!-- Hero Foundation Card -->
        <div class="foundation-hero">
          <h4>Product Surface Foundation</h4>
          <p>Everything starts here. Your business patterns, user needs, and technical constraints form the base every layer builds upon.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Layer Cards -->
        <div class="foundation-layer">
          <span class="layer-number">01</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">Communication</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">Aligning stakeholders on vision and goals</p>
        </div>

        <div class="foundation-layer">
          <span class="layer-number">02</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">Problem Statement</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">Defining what we're really solving</p>
        </div>

        <div class="foundation-layer">
          <span class="layer-number">03</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">Goal & Expectation</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">What success looks like for your business</p>
        </div>

        <div class="foundation-layer">
          <span class="layer-number">04</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">User Requirement</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">What users actually need to succeed</p>
        </div>

        <div class="foundation-layer">
          <span class="layer-number">05</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">Workflow</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">How this will work in practice</p>
        </div>

        <div class="foundation-layer data-layer">
          <span class="layer-number">06</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">Data Foundation</h5>
          <div class="data-badges">
            <span class="badge">Management</span>
            <span class="badge">Quality</span>
            <span class="badge">Privacy</span>
            <span class="badge">Compliance</span>
            <span class="badge">Data Steward</span>
            <span class="badge">Governance</span>
          </div>
          <p class="data-note">Maintenance | Improvement | Monitoring</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="methodology-note">
        Each layer builds on validated insights, not assumptions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .how-it-works .big-bold-text {
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .process-overview {
    background-color: var(--color-hover);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .process-overview h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .process-overview ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .process-overview li {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .process-overview li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent-warm);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .methodology {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: var(--space-4xl) auto 0;
  }

  .methodology h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .methodology-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  /* Foundation Stack - Modern Centerpiece Design */
  .foundation-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin: var(--space-4xl) 0;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  /* Foundation Hero Card */
  .foundation-hero {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 0 100px rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.4),
                0 8px 32px rgba(26, 58, 82, 0.3);
    animation: pulseGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeSlideUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.2s;
  }

  .foundation-hero h4 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .foundation-hero p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @keyframes pulseGlow {
    0%, 100% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 100px rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.4),
                  0 8px 32px rgba(26, 58, 82, 0.3);
    }
    50% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 120px rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.6),
                  0 8px 32px rgba(26, 58, 82, 0.3);
    }
  }

  /* Layer Cards */
  .foundation-layer {
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    position: relative;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeSlideUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .foundation-layer:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.7s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }

  .foundation-layer:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.3),
                0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  .layer-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--space-lg);
    left: var(--space-lg);
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--color-accent-warm);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .layer-title {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    margin-left: calc(48px + var(--space-lg));
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .layer-description {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-left: calc(48px + var(--space-lg));
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Data Layer Special Styling */
  .data-badges {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    margin-left: calc(48px + var(--space-lg));
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .badge:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-cool);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .data-note {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
    margin-left: calc(48px + var(--space-lg));
  }

  @keyframes fadeSlideUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .methodology-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent-warm);
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .foundation-hero h4 {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    }

    .layer-title {
      margin-left: 0;
      margin-top: calc(48px + var(--space-md));
    }

    .layer-description {
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    .layer-number {
      top: var(--space-md);
      left: var(--space-md);
    }

    .data-badges {
      margin-left: 0;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    .data-note {
      margin-left: 0;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Intersection Observer for scroll-triggered animation
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const stack = document.getElementById('foundation-stack');

    if (stack) {
      const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
        (entries) => {
          entries.forEach((entry) => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
              stack.classList.add('visible');
            }
          });
        },
        { threshold: 0.1 }
      );

      observer.observe(stack);
    }
  });
</script>
